<subSubSection id="6D872CC66B562DCDE607D46DD95FB9FE" pageId="0" pageNumber="27" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="C7E996615E78BCF6CDCAE577CC5F14F6" pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="669379A33C27C3736027C0B04373C5DF" pageId="0" pageNumber="27">South Africa, Gautan Province. Introduced, native to western Eurasia and North Africa, introduced to sub-Saharan Africa in Zimbabwe and South Africa.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
